    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "sure but \"avoiding future costs\" feels like a huge stretch when these guys are struggling to pay rent today. it feels like the gov is prioritizing these abstract long-term environmental goals over the actual survival of local businesses. isn't it a bit lopsided to assume the \"green tech sector\" is gonna pick up the slack for all the small shops that might actually go under because of this?",
